data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value: A futuristic lunar base dormitory with multiple individual sleeping pods arranged in a spacious, high-tech room. Each pod is cylindrical with transparent glass doors, equipped with a comfortable bed, pillows, and various integrated technologies, including digital control panels and ambient lighting. The floor is dark with some scattered pillows, and the ceiling is a textured dark metal, enhancing the space-age aesthetic. This setting conveys a blend of modern design and functionality suited for life on the moon
